== Creating global [[MIDI]] [[tempo]] changes in [[GarageBand]] ==

#Go to '''[[Track]]/Show Master Track''' and click it.
#In the master track that appears click the menu next to the speaker icon and select '''Master Tempo'''
#You can now create tempo changes by clicking the top of the purple tempo display that appears and move the [[node]]s up and down. Hold shift to move the nodes at finer values ( finer tempo changes)

